Author: bluediner
Text: I’m sorry to hear that :( if it makes you feel better, most of the time when I think I have a bad cut, it’s really just how different it is that upsets me, and the cut itself is usually fine! Hopefully both of us can move toward being kinder to ourselves though <3

Author: Throwthisaway512
Text: I feel that. A lady butchered my hair and gave me a emo mullet so I ugly cried the way home, put towels over the mirrors and just hit myself a bunch.   We can be our own worst enemy. I wish I knew how to fix it.
